<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to Flicker Frame!</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #2b2b2b;
      color: #e0e0e0;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      background: #3b3b3b;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }
    h1 {
      color: #81c784;
      font-size: 24px;
    }
    .otp {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #ffb74d;
    }
    .message {
      margin-top: 10px;
      color: #a0a0a0;
    }
    .footer {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #757575;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Welcome to Flicker Frame, <%= userName %>!</h1>
    
    <p>We’re excited to have you on board! Please use the following OTP to verify your account:</p>
    
    <p class="otp"><%= otp %></p>

    <p class="message">This OTP is valid for the next <%= expirationTime %> minutes.</p>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>If you didn’t request this email, please ignore it.</p>
      <p>Best regards,<br>The Flicker Frame Team</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
